---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="404 找不到頁面">
  <div class="outer-container">
    <img src="/theme/me.png" class="me" alt="" />
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-header default-background-header archive-header">
        <div class="header-inner">
          <div class="breadcrumb">
            <div class="breadcrumb-inner">
              <a href="/"><i class="fas fa-home"></i></a> &gt; 404
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="title-section">
            <h1 class="post-title">找不到頁面</h1>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <article class="post markdown-content" style="text-align: center;">
        <p>這個網址在封存版找不到對應的頁面。可能的原因：</p>
        <ul style="display: inline-block; text-align: left;">
          <li>原網站的連結結構未在此封存版重建</li>
          <li>該內容已從封存版中移除</li>
          <li>網址有誤</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="margin-top: 2em;">
          <a class="button404" href="/">回首頁</a>
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
